        "_account_id": 529,
        "name": "Ben Evans",
        "email": "beevans@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "bevans"
      },
      "date": "2017-12-08 14:25:32.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nAndreas, I'll dig into all of that, and see how much of it can be accomplished.  My main motivation for all this was making some sense of the way obd stats are done.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
